messages.speaker: agent
messages.text: Welcome! I'm Anita Bhargava, strategic financial advisor and co-founder of Bharosa Club. I'm excited to explore your financial journey together and help create a sustainable wealth-building strategy that aligns with your values and aspirations. Today, we'll focus on understanding your lifestyle preferences and goals - this foundation will be crucial for developing a personalized financial roadmap that truly works for you. Let's define success on your own terms. To get started, could you please tell me your name and age?
